<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> معجم البلدان لياقوت الحموى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> Muller: Die Burgen und Schlosser Sudarabiens nach dem Iklil des Hamdani in S. B. Ak. Wien, xciv. ١٨٧٩, p.٣٥٢ sqq<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> Azim al-Din Ahmad: Die auf Sudarabien bezuglichen Angaben Naswan's (G.M.S., xxiv., Leyden ١٩١٦), p ٣٠<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
